name: Launch On USD1
description: The Internet Capital Market, built on Ethereum and powered by USD1—a Trump-backed stablecoin from World Liberty Financial—enables anyone to launch, trade, and earn from tokens. The platform shares fees with creators, KOLs, and investors, fueling a meme-driven, community-powered economy. The platform is accessible via dApp, X (Twitter) Bot, Telegram Bot, and a mobile app, all enhanced by LLMs AI agents for a seamless Web3 experience.
